/*can not use dumpexfat for SD w/o exFAT*/
$ dumpexfat /dev/mmcblk0p1
dumpexfat 1.2.4
ERROR: exFAT file system is not found.

/*mount exFAT SD using mount.exfat*/
$ mount.exfat /dev/mmcblk0p2 /tmp/p2
FUSE exfat 1.2.4
$ ls /tmp/p2
check_fuse

